{"tid":755161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【放題店怪招】食客投訴用WeChat落單好麻煩 原來食店有苦衷？","createTime":"2018-07-25T03:46:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T06:11:24.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":66,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"7a7633d815f16cfeee6d920b0b0d3fd0fdd4aaff","tid":755161,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:46:06.000Z","msg":"從前去餐廳所有食物都由人手侍客、下單、上餐，不過隨着科技進步，以及愈來愈難請人的情況下，不少餐廳都選擇將下單過程電子化，例如以平板電腦或QR CODE代替人手下單，既可以節省時間也能解決人手不足的問題，但對於用家而言是否方便，則各有不同想法。<br />\n最近網上有人投訴，旺角有家火鍋放題店取消了劃紙仔下單的方法，取而代之要求客人使用內地聊天軟件WeChat或下載專用軟件以QR CODE下單。<br />\n細問之下，原來WeChat有份開發下單軟件「飯糰」，所以若然客人不想下載軟件，就只能使用WeChat的QR CODE掃描器。<br />\n而且當大家都以為以電話下單是為了讓店家節省金錢和時間，但就有店員表明最主要原因是因為長期聘請不到人手，無法應付餐廳工作，唯有出此下策。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_58474954\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fetw.nextdigital.com.hk%2Farticle%2F3_58474954&d=URtt3CCGnuGnLRHpeOfLmr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=fe966c2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://etw.nextdigital.com.hk/article/3_58474954</a>"},{"pid":"5b08148e187266cef0950895e6094bed34a932e5","tid":755161,"uid":77196,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:48:46.000Z","msg":"自己落單，但係都要俾加一間食肆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db49e69879a9f9de6f180982c4181ca35b030f03","tid":755161,"uid":52215,"like":7,"dislike":12,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:55:38.000Z","msg":"大陸好多餐廳都係自己用手機落單"},{"pid":"fe6799949c37202657642c975a1314a6ab96d079","tid":755161,"uid":43173,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:19:29.000Z","msg":"咁撚on9食店都唔好幫襯啦，苦乜撚嘢衷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c137ac7188b01347311a25da59e77caa0cd0c48c","tid":755161,"uid":33668,"like":6,"dislike":33,"score":-27,"quote":{"pid":"db49e69879a9f9de6f180982c4181ca35b030f03","tid":755161,"uid":52215,"like":7,"dislike":12,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:55:38.000Z","msg":"大陸好多餐廳都係自己用手機落單"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:25:51.000Z","msg":"其實香港呢一方面 真係好落後<br />\n<br />\n而且個出發點係為咗取代人手節省成本<br />\n<br />\n所以亦無香港公司DUM錢落去搞"},{"pid":"9487a6d3d8a9413268fcbbbb7f5369b2de75027d","tid":755161,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c137ac7188b01347311a25da59e77caa0cd0c48c","tid":755161,"uid":33668,"like":6,"dislike":33,"score":-27,"quote":{"pid":"db49e69879a9f9de6f180982c4181ca35b030f03","tid":755161,"uid":52215,"like":7,"dislike":12,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T03:55:38.000Z","msg":"大陸好多餐廳都係自己用手機落單"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:25:51.000Z","msg":"其實香港呢一方面 真係好落後<br />\n<br />\n而且個出發點係為咗取代人手節省成本<br />\n<br />\n所以亦無香港公司DUM錢落去搞"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:26:39.000Z","msg":"但另一邊<br />\n<br />\n搞得起可能會少好多樓面人手需求"},{"pid":"e0a9eec9d98cb39920bbc63ba08a8602cc81f53c","tid":755161,"uid":3241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:27:38.000Z","msg":"唔帶手機出街你連飯都冇得食呀........"},{"pid":"257465b45f90f44e2734ae35e4dd482cf305b8e6","tid":755161,"uid":34103,"like":4,"dislike":37,"score":-33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:28:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"acf3c0bf1690ad7acd943d06eaa949e32049afd3","tid":755161,"uid":42188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:31:41.000Z","msg":"餐廳：你唔鍾意可以唔食"},{"pid":"ae57a4f95e780d2fd266a00bae3e52307f6eeffc","tid":755161,"uid":147367,"like":32,"dislike":3,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:34:11.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，你要電子落單唔係問題<br />\n你咪自己買啲pad返黎俾入落單囉<br />\n<br />\n依家你請唔到人就要我用自己既資源去做啲你應該做既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c046c1169cbc8032b3f23823ec8a26c888e25b22","tid":755161,"uid":93784,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:42:27.000Z","msg":"好似元氣咁提供部機比你落單 <br />\n雖然部機有時都鳩鳩地另話 但做電子落單已經係最基本<br />\n點會要個客down app 仲要係wechat <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為左食野裝wechat 寧願去食第間<br />\n板長又係要裝佢公司app落單 麻煩呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d85d0e17f8cfa0625e35d37175cc2857de76d64","tid":755161,"uid":79410,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:50:28.000Z","msg":"但就有店員表明最主要原因是因為長期聘請不到人手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你2皮嘢請人我唔信請唔到。賺到盡就賺到盡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eb3b25a1c8372a5df6d5e86e6ba974a01dce685","tid":755161,"uid":6604,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"257465b45f90f44e2734ae35e4dd482cf305b8e6","tid":755161,"uid":34103,"like":4,"dislike":37,"score":-33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T04:28:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T05:03:49.000Z","msg":"因為你生活喺支那啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548d3faca96a47de219ed6137cdd0b4c6b7d2a13","tid":755161,"uid":42609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T05:11:29.000Z","msg":"板長之前都好似係用緊類似方式面落單<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知佢哋依家仲係咪咁"},{"pid":"db272de778601c3f832ee6e6dc4387451757518c","tid":755161,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T06:06:26.000Z","msg":"呢啲app 廿零三十萬有個，睇你做唔做姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814d0824f4db5e47bb27b6e2de866e8c87124e65","tid":755161,"uid":5490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-25T06:08:56.000Z","msg":"起身走人唔食啦，d野都唔知食唔食得既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee35cf9f691e92072b11428cc72cec2909c3a76","tid":755161,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,